name: Keeshond
description: Started as a meme token and acting as Samoyed's smaller brother of the Solana family! Like-minded people have come together to form a community, own and operate, made up exclusively of Keeshond Business owners. Our own members and benefactors interact within a decentralized and anonymous social media platform where KEESHOND visionaries and holders have access to. We like to share alerts, alpha news, joke, and grow together to enrich the Solana ecosystem.
